'''埃德·斯托帕德'''（'''Ed Stoppard'''，{{bd|1974年|9月16日}}）是[[英國|英國]]的一位演員。他的父親是劇作家[[湯姆·斯托帕德|湯姆·斯托帕德]]。斯托帕德和他的父親出身在一個猶太家庭<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jewish-theatre.com/visitor/article_display.aspx?articleID=1360 |title=All About Jewish Theatre – Tom Stoppard’s "Travesties" on Stage in Connecticut |publisher=Jewish-theatre.com |date=2005-06-05 |accessdate=2013-06-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220165649/http://www.jewish-theatre.com/visitor/article_display.aspx?articleID=1360 |archivedate=2013-12-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Julie McCaffrey |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/queen-honours-the-mirrors-dr-miriam-201271 |title=Queen honours The Mirror's Dr Miriam Stoppard with OBE – Mirror Online |publisher=Mirror.co.uk |date=2010-02-13 |accessdate=2013-06-22 |archive-date=2015-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224073608/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/queen-honours-the-mirrors-dr-miriam-201271 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾在[[愛丁堡大學|愛丁堡大學]]就讀法語。
